snippet.textDisplay: Story wise, I'm starting to get why they pick Mackie. Kinnaman was the best choice for Season 1 because he lost a lover and his sister some time before getting arrested and losing his 2nd lover. His cold and nihilistic feel shows his loss, and in the end of the season he finds out that Quell is still alive. Mackie would be a possible choice if you want someone with a bit of hope in his character. He'll probably have the same range of emotion as Lee in this season.
